How this possible?! Heruheru want
to send them to Mors and back!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0002
rows.name:
Survey team send word of ship that
have impertinence to do business
without approval of trade guild!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0003
rows.name:
If unlicensed trade allowed to
continue, marketplace end up in
complete shambles!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0004
rows.name:
And then that it! End of merchant
age! Lost in history!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0005
rows.name:
How about friends sneak on board
ship and leave them up creek without
paddle?

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0006
rows.name:
Splendid, splendid! Heruheru expect
to hear good news in near future!
